ACADEMIC / EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE
---------------------------------
This repository is a derivative work produced for academic and educational
purposes as part of an MS thesis ("Global Context-Aware Neural Cellular Automata
for Brain Tumor Segmentation"). It is provided for research, study and teaching
only. It is NOT a medical device and MUST NOT be used for clinical diagnosis,
treatment, or any real-world patient-care decision.

The thesis modifications (BraTS multi-modal pipeline, the global-context SE
block, multi-class WT/TC/ET segmentation, evaluation metrics, and related code)
are released under the MIT License below.

    Copyright (c) 2025 Muhammad Waqas

This work builds on the original Med-NCA / M3D-NCA framework, whose copyright
notice is retained as required by its MIT License:

    Copyright (c) 2023 John Kalkhof

Both copyright notices must be preserved in all copies or substantial portions
of the Software.

